---

<Layout
  title="Kids Activation & Events Specialist in Melbourne | Fizz Kidz"
  description="Fizz Kidz runs activations and events across Australia, creating a space for children to create something special. Book us for your shopping center, corporate event or anywhere you need a little bit of Fizz!"
>
  <main>
    <div class="m-auto block max-w-[1380px] px-5 pt-4">
      <div class="h-[10px]"></div>
      <BreadcrumbWrapper
        items={[
          {
            type: "link",
            path: "/activations-and-events/",
            title: "Activations and Events",
          },
        ]}
      />
      <PageIntro
        subtitle="Seriously fun activations!"
        type="image"
        image={hero}
        imageAlt="Fizz Kids running a beautiful activation in a shopping center"
        actionButtonText="Book an activation or event"
        actionButtonPath="#contact"
        color="blue"
      >
        <span slot="title">Kids Activations and Events in Melbourne</span>
        <span slot="content"
          >Fizz Kidz is an innovative and vibrant company that is wholeheartedly
          dedicated to providing high-energy, interactive and fun experiences
          for children. Fizz Kidz Activations are vibrant and engaging,
          fostering a sense of wonder and creating a world of curious excitement
          for children.</span
        >
      </PageIntro>
      <section class="mt-28 lg:mt-40">
        <h5 class="text-center font-lilita text-5xl">
          Share the Fizz and create a buzz around your community!
        </h5>
        <div class="mt-20 flex flex-col gap-8 lg:mt-28 lg:gap-16">
          <WideImageCard
            image={mCity}
            imageAlt="Fiz Kidz running programs for children in a large shopping center with balloons"
            imageSide="left"
          >
            <div
              slot="content"
              class="flex h-full flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8"
            >
              <h6 class="text-center font-lilita text-4xl text-[#4DC5D9]">
                School Holiday Activations
              </h6>
              <p class="text-center font-gotham font-medium leading-8">
                Join us for school holiday fun! Choose from our pre-created
                themes or share your vision, and we'll bring it to life. Whether
                it's for one or two weeks, we've got you covered.
              </p>
            </div>
          </WideImageCard>
          <WideImageCard
            image={kidsMornings}
            imageAlt="A child smiling while drawing with crayons"
            imageSide="right"
          >
            <div
              slot="content"
              class="flex h-full flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8"
            >
              <h6 class="text-center font-lilita text-4xl text-[#4FE16D]">
                Pre-school Kids Mornings
              </h6>
              <p class="text-center font-gotham font-medium leading-8">
                Bring weekday morning excitement to your Centre. Little ones and
                parents join in for fun developmentally appropriate activities
                that families love! Choose from our pre-planned workshops or
                we'll customise the sessions to your vision!
              </p>
            </div>
          </WideImageCard>
          <WideImageCard
            image={mothersDayClassic}
            imageAlt="Fizz Kids building cardboard houses outdoors with a marquee in the background"
            imageSide="left"
          >
            <div
              slot="content"
              class="flex h-full flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8"
            >
              <h6 class="text-center font-lilita text-4xl text-[#4DC5D9]">
                Corporate Events
              </h6>
              <p class="text-center font-gotham font-medium leading-8">
                Elevate your corporate events with Fizz Kidz! Your team and
                customers will love you for it. Whether it's a company family
                fun day, a public showcase, or a large-scale pop-up event, we
                deliver high-end, seamless, and beloved activations!
              </p>
            </div>
          </WideImageCard>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <div class="mt-28 bg-[#EBFAFE] p-4">
          <h6 class="pb-2 pl-12 pt-12 font-lilita text-4xl text-[#6EC1E4]">
            Calendar Themed Activations
          </h6>
          <CardCarousel
            client:visible
            items={[
              {
                title: "Mothers Day",
                content:
                  "An activation wrapped in pastel pinks, designed to celebrate mums! This event offers a variety of activities for kids that are sure to delight mums, from creating Mother's Day cards to making bath bombs. It's an activation guaranteed to bring smiles to all.",
                image: mothersDayOptimised,
                imageAlt: "A child colouring in a card for mothers day",
                buttonText: "Book Now",
                buttonPath: "#contact",
              },
              {
                title: "Exciting Easter",
                content:
                  "Spring into fun with our Easter-themed activations where kids create truly egg-citing activities! Activities include Easter Baskets, Easter Egg Bath-Bombs and Bunny Ears.",
                image: easterOptimised,
                imageAlt: "An crafty easter egg",
                buttonText: "Book Now",
                buttonPath: "#contact",
              },
              {
                title: "Christmas Cheer",
                content:
                  "Spread the Holiday Spirit! In this Activation kids craft festive Christmas activities, including Christmas Stockings, Snow Houses and Christmas Slime.",
                image: christmasOptimised,
                imageAlt: "A child making a cutout christmas tree",
                buttonText: "Book Now",
                buttonPath: "#contact",
              },
              {
                title: "Haunted Halloween",
                content:
                  "Step into a Spooky Spectacle! Kids craft up their spooky activities including Monster Slime and Wild Animal Masks.",
                image: halloweenOptimised,
                imageAlt: "A slimey couldron",
                buttonText: "Book Now",
                buttonPath: "#contact",
              },
              {
                title: "Back to School",
                content:
                  "Get kids and families into your centre for back to school shopping with school themed kids activities!",
                image: backToSchoolOptimised,
                imageAlt: "A kid carefully reading from an instruction booklet",
                buttonText: "Book Now",
                buttonPath: "#contact",
              },
              {
                title: "Science Week",
                content:
                  "This Activation is scientifically fantastic offering kids hands-on science experiments to make and take home with them for hours of fun!",
                image: scienceWeekOptimised,
                imageAlt: "A child playing with slime they made",
                buttonText: "Book Now",
                buttonPath: "#contact",
              },
            ]}
          />
        </div>
        <div class="p-4">
          <h6 class="pb-2 pl-12 pt-12 font-lilita text-4xl text-[#6EC1E4]">
            Themed Activations
          </h6>
          <CardCarousel
            client:visible
            items={[
              {
                title: "Silly Scientist",
                content:
                  "A Fizz Kidz favourite, this activation is scientifically-fantastic! Kids get hands-on making their own science experiments lead by enthusiastic facilitators dressed in lab coats and science goggles.",
                image: scientistOptimised,
                imageAlt: "A kid in a lab coat pouring something",
                buttonText: "Book Now",
                buttonPath: "#contact",
              },
              {
                title: "Winter Wonderland",
                content:
                  "Step into the winter wonderland! Kids explore enchanting activities like instant snow slime, frosty bath-bombs and build their own snow houses.",
                image: winterWonderlandOptimised,
                imageAlt: "White snow slime",
                buttonText: "Book Now",
                buttonPath: "#contact",
              },
              {
                title: "Roaring Rainbows",
                content:
                  "Our Roaring Rainbows activation is a colourful celebration packed with vibrant activities, including rainbow wall hangings, rainbow and rainbow sand art.",
                image: rainbowsOptimised,
                imageAlt: "A Fizz Kids staff holding crafted rainbows",
                buttonText: "Book Now",
                buttonPath: "#contact",
              },
              {
                title: "Excellent Engineers",
                content:
                  "This activation is packed with hands-on activities and challenges designed to spark creativity and problem-solving skills. Activities include 3D roller coasters, catapults and parachutes.",
                image: engineersOptimised,
                imageAlt: "Two kids laughing with bath bombs",
                buttonText: "Book Now",
                buttonPath: "#contact",
              },
              {
                title: "Enchanted Forest",
                content:
                  "Step into the whimsical enchanted forest with us! This activation has kids making magic sand, creatures-of-the-night masks, monster slime and more.",
                image: heroOptimised,
                imageAlt: "An crafty easter egg",
                buttonText: "Book Now",
                buttonPath: "#contact",
              },
              {
                title: "Amazing Animals",
                content:
                  "Join us as we explore the fascinating world of animals through hands-on activities such as dinosaur eggs, hamster pencil holders and bugs in bath-bombs.",
                image: animalsOptimised,
                imageAlt: "A toy dinosaur in a bath bomb",
                buttonText: "Book Now",
                buttonPath: "#contact",
              },
            ]}
          />
        </div>
      </section>
      <section
        class="my-12 flex flex-col-reverse gap-8 md:pb-12 md:pt-16 lg:flex-row"
      >
        <div class="px-0 sm:px-12 lg:w-1/2">
          <Image
            class="rounded-2xl object-contain shadow-green-sm sm:shadow-green-md"
            src={staffArchway}
            alt="Two Fizz Kids staff standing under an archway"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="flex w-full flex-col justify-center gap-4 lg:w-1/2">
          <p class="text-center font-lilita text-5xl lg:text-start">
            From big to small, we have you covered.
          </p>
          <p class="text-center font-gotham text-lg lg:text-start">
            Whether you're looking for a one-stop shop or have the
            infrastructure yourselves and need us to run amazing daily
            activities; we're experts in kids' entertainment and we will work
            with you to bring your vision to life.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h6 class="my-20 text-center font-lilita text-6xl">
          You're in great company!
        </h6>
        <LogoGrid client:visible logos={logos} />
      </section>
      <section>
        <Reviews
          title="Hear what our partners have to say!"
          reviews={[
            {
              review:
                "Engaging Minecraft activation captivating kids and parents, with a friendly and proactive team. Meticulous planning and flexibility led to a positive experience for all participants, resulting in a great turnout and consistent engagement - loved every moment! ðŸŒŸ",
              writtenBy: "Genny, Sanctuary Lakes Shopping Center",
              writtenYear: "2024",
            },
            {
              review:
                "This was our first time collaborating with Fizz Kids for an activity at CS Square shopping centre. We were very happy from the start of our inquiry to the end of the activity. The team were prompt with their communication and Customer facing was very professional yet fun. We will definitely be looking at more activations from them in the future!",
              writtenBy: "Patric, SC Square",
              writtenYear: "2024",
            },
          ]}
        />
      </section>
    </div>
    <section class="relative mt-12">
      <Image
        class="min-h-[320px] w-full object-cover"
        src={staff}
        alt="full width image of Fizz Kids staff smiling"
      />
      <div
        class="absolute right-0 top-1/2 my-auto w-2/3 -translate-y-[40%] min-[450px]:w-1/2"
      >
        <div class="flex max-w-[420px] flex-col gap-6 p-4">
          <p class="font-lilita text-xl md:text-4xl">Have an idea in mind?</p>
          <p class="font- text-sm font-semibold text-white md:text-xl">
            Let us know your vision and our amazing design team will bring it to
            life!
          </p>
          <PrimaryButton
            text="Let's talk today!"
            path="#contact"
            className="w-fit"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="contact"></div>
    </section>
    <section class="m-auto mt-12 block max-w-3xl px-5 py-8">
      <p class="mb-4 text-center font-lilita text-4xl">
        Contact us - we're friendly!
      </p>
      <p class="text-center font-gotham text-base font-semibold">
        Please let us know what type of activation or event your looking to run
        and we will get back to you with all our details.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p class="mb-8 text-center font-gotham text-base font-semibold">
        Please include your preferred dates.
      </p>
      <ActivationsForm client:visible />
    </section>
    <Values />
  </main>
</Layout>
